---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="bg-primary-dark/95 text-white border-t border-accent/15 py-5" aria-label="Patented technology">
  <Container class="flex items-start gap-3 reveal">
    <span class="shrink-0 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-accent/15">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M8 2L10 6L14 7L11 10L12 14L8 12L4 14L5 10L2 7L6 6Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </span>
    <p class="text-[13px] text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
      <strong class="text-accent">Certified excellence:</strong>
      Empereal's water and desalination systems are delivered under
      <strong class="text-white">ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015, and ISO 45001:2018</strong>
      certified management systems — ensuring rigorous quality assurance, environmental responsibility, and safety across every project.
    </p>
  </Container>
</section>
